    "body": "That is pretty much the right idea, but there is an important point that you will need to consider and change.  When you have a line like `line.GetText = () => FieldLoader.Translate(\"STRING-ID\")` this is actually a function that is called every time the game renders.  You really don't want to be retranslating these strings 60 times per second!\r\n\r\nInstead use a pattern like this:\r\n```csharp\r\nvar translatedStringID = FieldLoader.Translate(\"STRING-ID\");\r\nline.GetText = () => translatedStringID;\r\n```\r\n\r\nWe will also need to support for map-defined translations, so your changes to `LoadTranslations` will need to be reworked."
  },
